race.comment: PARIS WILL WAIT (6) is generally an honest type in the frame at 16 of 53 starts but missed the placings last time when fourth (16.97) over 300m at Q Straight. Solid record at this trip including 11 wins. Looks the testing material here. GOLDSTAR SUMMER (2) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (19.85) from Box 5 at this track. Has a strong record out of this box with five wins and a minor placing from nine starts. Must be included in calculations. FARMOR ENVY (1) went straight to the front and never headed when winning two back but could manage only midfield last time when finished 6th and beaten 10 lengths at this track (20.15). Has ability and a bold showing is expected. SPRING TARA (7) has won at this course and distance, should be thereabouts.
